:"2020-07-16T05:45:15.000Z","msg":"借個位 保安局發出超過20萬張豁免強制檢疫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2106369/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2106369/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家支持廣傳消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔自救大家玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我哋可以做咩嘢？</span></span></strong><br />\n1.話比身邊嘅人知香港有個後門大量吸收潛在冇病症感染者及傳播者。<br />\n<br />\n2.呼籲身邊所有人戴口罩，特別係果班唔肯帶嘅中年人<br />\n<br />\n3.如果身邊有料，可以報上傳媒比如蘋果。<br />\n例如喺之前post有其他人話知道：<br />\n灣仔入境個邊D移民公司而家當免檢疫証明係生意咁做，搵班阿姐派傳單幫人攪。<br />\n每日中港司機都幾千人出出入入。<br />\n<br />\n4.煲大件事！比全世界多D人知道，只有多D人覺醒，知道個政府係棄全香港巿民安危不顧，先會爭取到更多人企係我哋呢邊，同我哋一齊抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟姊妹各自爬山 他日平安相聚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c249cdea18338be735c8d132cae35446f63f6f","tid":2110634,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"me in mtr yelled wear your fucking mask<br />\n<br />\nit works like charm"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8754593887c14ed790a2f44f9f38a5431df5fd8c","tid":2110634,"uid":224234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:36:55.000Z","msg":"點解問呢個問題？<br />\n<br />\nfb唔少 group其實都有兩派人喺度拗緊呢個問題：到底防疫緊要啲定係個人選擇緊要啲"}}